Built for Whats Next

Doodles is a next-generation entertainment company building immersive storytelling experiences through original content, music, digital collectibles, live activations, and lifestyle products.

Stories in Motion

Where Doodles Meets Culture

Alongside our award-winning creative agency, Golden Wolf, and our audio studio, Take Your Medicine, we bring 360 campaigns to life for partners like McDonalds, Kelloggs, Adidas Originals, AriZona Beverages, G-SHOCK, and more, delivering storytelling that spans content, experiences, and culture.

Built Together

Our secret sauce.

Our community is made up of tens of thousands of dedicated supporters whove made Doodles what it is today. Theyre not just fans or followers, theyre creators, collectors, and ambassadors who shape the culture around Doodles.

From sparking viral moments on social media, to showing up at global events, our community is the fuel that drives us to keep pushing the envelope, ensuring Doodles is built with its community, not just for it.
